   },
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/html": [
       "\n",
       "<table style=\"width: 100%;\"><tr><td>simpleRNASeq,BamFileList,RnaSeqParam-method {easyRNASeq}</td><td style=\"text-align: right;\">R Documentation</td></tr></table>\n",
       "\n",
       "<h2 id='simpleRNASeq+2CBamFileList+2CRnaSeqParam-method'>simpleRNASeq method</h2>\n",
       "\n",
       "<h3>Description</h3>\n",
       "\n",
       "<p>This function is a wrapper around the more low level functionalities of the\n",
       "package. It is the simplest way to get a <code>RangedSummarizedExperiment</code>\n",
       "object from a set of bam files. <code>RangedSummarizedExperiment</code> are\n",
       "containers meant to hold any Next-Generation Sequencing experiment results and\n",
       "metadata. The simpleRNASeq method replaces the\n",
       "<code>easyRNASeq</code> function to\n",
       "simplify the usability. It does the following:\n",
       "</p>\n",
       "\n",
       "<ul>\n",
       "<li><p> use <code>GenomicAlignments</code>\n",
       "for reading/pre-processing the BAM files.\n",
       "</p>\n",
       "</li>\n",
       "<li><p> get the <code>annotations</code>\n",
       "depending on the selected parameters\n",
       "</p>\n",
       "</li>\n",
       "<li><p> calculate the coverage from the provided file(s)\n",
       "</p>\n",
       "</li>\n",
       "<li> <p><code>summarizes</code> the\n",
       "read counts according to the selected summarization\n",
       "</p>\n",
       "</li>\n",
       "<li><p> returns a <code>RangedSummarizedExperiment</code> object.\n",
       "</p>\n",
       "</li></ul>\n",
       "\n",
       "\n",
       "\n",
       "<h3>Usage</h3>\n",
       "\n",
       "<pre><code class='language-R'>## S4 method for signature 'BamFileList,RnaSeqParam'\n",
       "simpleRNASeq(\n",
       "  bamFiles = BamFileList(),\n",
       "  param = RnaSeqParam(),\n",
       "  nnodes = 1,\n",
       "  verbose = TRUE,\n",
       "  override = FALSE\n",
       ")\n",
       "</code></pre>\n",
       "\n",
       "\n",
       "<h3>Arguments</h3>\n",
       "\n",
       "<table>\n",
       "<tr><td><code id=\"simpleRNASeq+2CBamFileList+2CRnaSeqParam-method_:_bamFiles\">bamFiles</code></td>\n",
       "<td>\n",
       "<p>a <code>BamFileList</code> object</p>\n",
       "</td></tr>\n",
       "<tr><td><code id=\"simpleRNASeq+2CBamFileList+2CRnaSeqParam-method_:_param\">param</code></td>\n",
       "<td>\n",
       "<p>RnaSeqParam a <code>RnaSeqParam</code> object\n",
       "that describes the RNA-Seq experimental setup.</p>\n",
       "</td></tr>\n",
       "<tr><td><code id=\"simpleRNASeq+2CBamFileList+2CRnaSeqParam-method_:_nnodes\">nnodes</code></td>\n",
       "<td>\n",
       "<p>The number of CPU cores to use in parallel</p>\n",
       "</td></tr>\n",
       "<tr><td><code id=\"simpleRNASeq+2CBamFileList+2CRnaSeqParam-method_:_verbose\">verbose</code></td>\n",
       "<td>\n",
       "<p>a logical to be report progress or not.</p>\n",
       "</td></tr>\n",
       "<tr><td><code id=\"simpleRNASeq+2CBamFileList+2CRnaSeqParam-method_:_override\">override</code></td>\n",
       "<td>\n",
       "<p>Should the provided parameters override the detected ones</p>\n",
       "</td></tr>\n",
       "</table>\n",
       "\n",
       "\n",
       "<h3>Value</h3>\n",
       "\n",
       "<p>returns a <code>RangedSummarizedExperiment</code> object.\n",
       "</p>\n",
       "\n",
       "\n",
       "<h3>Author(s)</h3>\n",
       "\n",
       "<p>Nicolas Delhomme\n",
       "</p>\n",
       "\n",
       "\n",
       "<h3>See Also</h3>\n",
       "\n",
       "\n",
       "<ul>\n",
       "<li><p>For the input:\n",
       "</p>\n",
       "\n",
       "<ul>\n",
       "<li> <p><code>AnnotParam</code>\n",
       "</p>\n",
       "</li>\n",
       "<li> <p><code>BamParam</code>\n",
       "</p>\n",
       "</li>\n",
       "<li> <p><code>RnaSeqParam</code>\n",
       "</p>\n",
       "</li></ul>\n",
       "\n",
       "</li>\n",
       "<li><p>For the output:\n",
       "<code>RangedSummarizedExperiment</code>\n",
       "\n",
       "</p>\n",
       "</li>\n",
       "<li><p>For related functions:\n",
       "</p>\n",
       "\n",
       "<ul>\n",
       "<li> <p><code>BamFile</code>\n",
       "</p>\n",
       "</li>\n",
       "<li> <p><code>BamFileList</code>\n",
       "<code>getBamFileList</code>\n",
       "</p>\n",
       "</li></ul>\n",
       "\n",
       "</li></ul>\n",
       "\n",
       "\n",
       "\n",
       "<h3>Examples</h3>\n",
       "\n",
       "<pre><code class='language-R'>\n",
       "# the data\n",
       "tdir &lt;- tutorialData()\n",
       "annot &lt;- fetchData(\"Drosophila_melanogaster.BDGP5.77.with-chr.gtf.gz\")\n",
       "\n",
       " # create the BamFileList, get the BAM and BAI index files from the Bioc cache\n",
       " filenames &lt;- dir(tdir,pattern=\"[A,T].*\\\\.bam$\",full.names=TRUE)\n",
       " indexnames &lt;- sapply(paste0(sub(\".*_\",\"\",basename(filenames)),\".bai\"),fetchData)\n",
       " bamFiles &lt;- getBamFileList(filenames,indexnames)\n",
       "\n",
       "  # create the AnnotParam\n",
       "  annotParam &lt;- AnnotParam(annot,type=\"gtf\")\n",
       "\n",
       "  # create the RnaSeqParam\n",
       "  rnaSeqParam &lt;- RnaSeqParam(annotParam=annotParam)\n",
       "\n",
       "  # get a RangedSummarizedExperiment containing the counts table\n",
       "  sexp &lt;- simpleRNASeq(\n",
       "    bamFiles=bamFiles,\n",
       "    param=rnaSeqParam,\n",
       "    verbose=TRUE\n",
       "  )\n",
       "\n",
       "  # get the counts\n",
       "  assays(sexp)$exons\n",
       "\n",
       "</code></pre>\n",
       "\n",
       "<hr /><div style=\"text-align: center;\">[Package <em>easyRNASeq</em> version 2.36.0 ]</div>\n",
       "</div>"
      ],
      "text/latex": [
       "\\inputencoding{utf8}\n",
       "\\HeaderA{simpleRNASeq,BamFileList,RnaSeqParam-method}{simpleRNASeq method}{simpleRNASeq,BamFileList,RnaSeqParam.Rdash.method}\n",
       "\\aliasA{simpleRNASeq}{simpleRNASeq,BamFileList,RnaSeqParam-method}{simpleRNASeq}\n",
       "\\keyword{methods}{simpleRNASeq,BamFileList,RnaSeqParam-method}\n",
       "%\n",
       "\\begin{Description}\n",
       "This function is a wrapper around the more low level functionalities of the\n",
       "package. It is the simplest way to get a \\code{\\LinkA{RangedSummarizedExperiment}{RangedSummarizedExperiment.Rdash.class}}\n",
       "object from a set of bam files. \\code{\\LinkA{RangedSummarizedExperiment}{RangedSummarizedExperiment.Rdash.class}} are\n",
       "containers meant to hold any Next-Generation Sequencing experiment results and\n",
       "metadata. The simpleRNASeq method replaces the\n",
       "\\code{\\LinkA{easyRNASeq}{easyRNASeq}} function to\n",
       "simplify the usability. It does the following:\n",
       "\\begin{itemize}\n",
       "\n",
       "\\item{} use \\code{\\LinkA{GenomicAlignments}{GenomicAlignments}}\n",
       "for reading/pre-processing the BAM files.\n",
       "\\item{} get the \\code{\\LinkA{annotations}{annotations}}\n",
       "depending on the selected parameters\n",
       "\\item{} calculate the coverage from the provided file(s)\n",
       "\\item{} \\code{\\LinkA{summarizes}{summarizes}} the\n",
       "read counts according to the selected summarization\n",
       "\\item{} returns a \\code{\\LinkA{RangedSummarizedExperiment}{RangedSummarizedExperiment.Rdash.class}} object.\n",
       "\n",
       "\\end{itemize}\n",
       "\n",
       "\\end{Description}\n",
       "%\n",
       "\\begin{Usage}\n",
       "\\begin{verbatim}\n",
       "## S4 method for signature 'BamFileList,RnaSeqParam'\n",
       "simpleRNASeq(\n",
       "  bamFiles = BamFileList(),\n",
       "  param = RnaSeqParam(),\n",
       "  nnodes = 1,\n",
       "  verbose = TRUE,\n",
       "  override = FALSE\n",
       ")\n",
       "\\end{verbatim}\n",
       "\\end{Usage}\n",
       "%\n",
       "\\begin{Arguments}\n",
       "\\begin{ldescription}\n",
       "\\item[\\code{bamFiles}] a \\code{\\LinkA{BamFileList}{BamFileList.Rdash.class}} object\n",
       "\n",
       "\\item[\\code{param}] RnaSeqParam a \\code{\\LinkA{RnaSeqParam}{RnaSeqParam.Rdash.class}} object\n",
       "that describes the RNA-Seq experimental setup.\n",
       "\n",
       "\\item[\\code{nnodes}] The number of CPU cores to use in parallel\n",
       "\n",
       "\\item[\\code{verbose}] a logical to be report progress or not.\n",
       "\n",
       "\\item[\\code{override}] Should the provided parameters override the detected ones\n",
       "\\end{ldescription}\n",
       "\\end{Arguments}\n",
       "%\n",
       "\\begin{Value}\n",
       "returns a \\code{\\LinkA{RangedSummarizedExperiment}{RangedSummarizedExperiment.Rdash.class}} object.\n",
       "\\end{Value}\n",
       "%\n",
       "\\begin{Author}\n",
       "Nicolas Delhomme\n",
       "\\end{Author}\n",
       "%\n",
       "\\begin{SeeAlso}\n",
       "\\begin{itemize}\n",
       "\n",
       "\\item{} For the input:\n",
       "\\begin{itemize}\n",
       "\n",
       "\\item{} \\code{\\LinkA{AnnotParam}{AnnotParam.Rdash.class}}\n",
       "\\item{} \\code{\\LinkA{BamParam}{BamParam.Rdash.class}}\n",
       "\\item{} \\code{\\LinkA{RnaSeqParam}{RnaSeqParam.Rdash.class}}\n",
       "\n",
       "\\end{itemize}\n",
       "\n",
       "\\item{} For the output:\n",
       "\\code{\\LinkA{RangedSummarizedExperiment}{RangedSummarizedExperiment.Rdash.class}}\n",
       "\n",
       "\\item{} For related functions:\n",
       "\\begin{itemize}\n",
       "\n",
       "\\item{} \\code{\\LinkA{BamFile}{BamFile.Rdash.class}}\n",
       "\\item{} \\code{\\LinkA{BamFileList}{BamFileList.Rdash.class}}\n",
       "\\code{\\LinkA{getBamFileList}{getBamFileList}}\n",
       "\n",
       "\\end{itemize}\n",
       "\n",
       "\n",
       "\\end{itemize}\n",
       "\n",
       "\\end{SeeAlso}\n",
       "%\n",
       "\\begin{Examples}\n",
       "\\begin{ExampleCode}\n",
       "\n",
       "# the data\n",
       "tdir <- tutorialData()\n",
       "annot <- fetchData(\"Drosophila_melanogaster.BDGP5.77.with-chr.gtf.gz\")\n",
       "\n",
       " # create the BamFileList, get the BAM and BAI index files from the Bioc cache\n",
       " filenames <- dir(tdir,pattern=\"[A,T].*\\\\.bam$\",full.names=TRUE)\n",
       " indexnames <- sapply(paste0(sub(\".*_\",\"\",basename(filenames)),\".bai\"),fetchData)\n",
       " bamFiles <- getBamFileList(filenames,indexnames)\n",
       "\n",
       "  # create the AnnotParam\n",
       "  annotParam <- AnnotParam(annot,type=\"gtf\")\n",
       "\n",
       "  # create the RnaSeqParam\n",
       "  rnaSeqParam <- RnaSeqParam(annotParam=annotParam)\n",
       "\n",
       "  # get a RangedSummarizedExperiment containing the counts table\n",
